name: DigitalDashboardPluginLifeTable
description: Visualization component for the old version of the DigitalDashboard. Expects to be connected as a child to the DigitalDashboard Webble. Draws 'Life Tables', which means it plots the number of (or % of) patients in the data that are still alive (or still relapse free etc.) as a function of time.
author: legacyDigitalDashboard
